{"type": "article", "id": 23277, "title": "可充电的椅子", "description": "", "date": "2016-03-04T07:30:16Z", "super_tag": "", "tags": [], "category": 25, "column": 28, "author": 161922, "comment_count": 2, "praise_count": 17, "image": "img/article/article_show/20160606152444KPhTNFCiSpk0scLU.jpeg", "contents": "\n\n<p class=\"\">这是一把可以为手机充电的椅子，名字“moov”就是移动（move）的意思。椅子的外形很简单，由榉木和悬臂钢架组成。荷兰设计师 Nathalie Teugels 利用了压电效应，在椅子上安装传感器，当让坐在椅子上或者移动椅子，就能激活传感器发电。蓝色的悬臂也是 USB 接口，直接连接到手机上充电。<a href=\"http://nteugels.tumblr.com/prototype\">点击这里可以查看更多信息。</a><br></p>\n<div class=\"com-insert-images medium-insert-active medium-insert-images-wide\">\n<figure class=\"\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20160606152442m1VOa9lR5IT2ZJD6.jpg\" alt=\"\" class=\"medium-insert-image-active\" data-ratio=\"0.66625917\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n<figcaption class=\"medium-insert-caption-placeholder\"></figcaption></figure><figure class=\"\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20160606152442ZqUrETH1Lo2eO9tF.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"1.5\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/201606061524421lAgsqnF2Ee5N9Oh.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.66625917\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/201606061524437H4vz5KtNrVPg9pS.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.66625917\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20160606152443Cgu1Pd2eQJASE6NI.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"1.12591687\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure>\n</div>\n\n\n"}